abstract: Stocks end flat after week of gains, offset by lower oil prices.
lead_paragraph: G.D.P. in the United States rose more than expected. And despite a lackluster day, stocks ended the week with a second straight weekly gain.

headline.main: Market Little Changed Despite Strong Economic Data
